38 Department of Agriculture Food and Nutrition Service.
39 (b) The commissioner of the department shall request a
40 waiver from the USDA Food and Nutrition Service to authorize
41 the department to add hot rotisserie chickens to the
42 definition of "eligible foods" under 7 C.F.R. ยง 271.2.
